column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,  p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  p.score, p.type, s.class, s.subclass, FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  p.score > #  AND p.CLEAN = #  AND p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.g BETWEEN # AND # ORDER BY p.field
